title: [PSP] 3.90 M33-2 Custom Firmware Pack
description:
3.90 M33-2 Custom Firmware Pack


   Includes:

     - 3.90 M33-2 by Dark~AleX with the 390.PBP included in the installer.

     - 3.71 fatmsmod patch by Dark~AleX with fatmsmod.prx included.

     - 3.80 popsloader plugin v2 by Dark~AleX (compatible with 3.90 M33-2) including
       all firmware modules.

     - 1.50 kernel add-on v2 for Fat/PSP-1000 models for 3.90 M33 with 150.PBP
       included.

     - MAC Address spoofer plugin by Dark~AleX.

     - CWCheat 2.1.0 Revision A by Wetall.
